         AIF   (T'&LENGTH EQ 'O').RSVERR1 NO LENGTH SPECIFIED - ERROR   01300000
         AIF   ('&LENGTH'(1,2) EQ '(R').RSV100 REGISTER NOTATION?       01350000
         LA    R1,&LENGTH          LOAD LENGTH IN REGISTER 1            01400000
